{"tid":2190694,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"巴西男女國腳同工同酬","createTime":"2020-09-06T02:11:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-06T03:32:36.000Z","uid":49776,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3a2f06119b69fc6bde1cee5905d441dcd7d2c810","tid":2190694,"uid":49776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T02:11:33.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports】巴西足總於周三宣佈，加入男子及女子國腳代表國家隊出場酬勞看齊的行列。<br />\n巴西足總會長卡布路於周三宣佈，以後男子與女子國腳代表國家隊出賽的酬勞將會一樣，換言之，一眾女國腳出場的酬勞，與巨星尼馬別無兩樣。巴西男足曾贏過5次世界盃，而女足亦不失禮，曾殺入女足世界盃、奧運的決賽。 巴西可不是創這個男女國腳同工同酬的先河，因為澳洲、挪威與新西蘭早就列明兩性國腳代表國家隊出賽的酬勞相同。去年3月，世界冠軍美國女足入稟控告美國足總不同酬勞涉及歧視敗訴，但已提出上訴。 球壇男女子不同待遇的現象一直存在，而車路士女足日前以35萬歐元羅致丹麥國腳赫達，刷新女足的轉會費紀錄，但與男足球員轉會費相比是九牛一毛。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/FIFAWWC/status/1301268456671784962\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FFIFAWWC%2Fstatus%2F1301268456671784962&d=bvaV6%2BUCrkGuzNdoarVmRw1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=5c10bcff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FFIFAWWC%2Fstatus%2F1301268456671784962&h=7c155ad7\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/FIFAWWC/status/1301268456671784962</a>"},{"pid":"99f1448bcced4cc34c1f71df669fa6c452ffdae8","tid":2190694,"uid":171278,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T02:12:58.000Z","msg":"明明女足既技術水平比男足差幾條街 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f18ba174350c5b646b493e4ff7a0036f144f41a6","tid":2190694,"uid":312758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T02:15:50.000Z","msg":"巴西足球玩撚猿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05e9fb91c39c3bf947dc3ea8d7a24c0e8d8406d0","tid":2190694,"uid":158876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T02:16:52.000Z","msg":"剩係國家隊je&hellip;"},{"pid":"1a26faaf35eff5d3855f995a21e32c665985b87c","tid":2190694,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T02:41:55.000Z","msg":"留名等睇冇男人肯入國家隊<img src=\"/as